title: Your Second Rate Podcast Is Dead 12/18: Dr. Jill Biden, Cyberpunk 2077 (sorry), Madalorian, Mike Pence, Jerry West, the Paul brothers
itunes:title: Your Second Rate Podcast Is Dead 12/18: Dr. Jill Biden, Cyberpunk 2077 (sorry), Madalorian, Mike Pence, Jerry West, the Paul brothers
description:
On this edition of Your Second Rate Podcast Is Dead Jack and Miles discuss Dr. Jill Biden going on Colbert to discuss the WSJ article, Cyberpunk 2077 is getting pulled from the online stores of the PS4 and Xbox One for misconstruing consumers, the Mandalorian season 2 has concluded (neither of the boys watched), Mike Pence got the vaccine on camera, Jerry West and the Clippers org are being investigated regarding the Kawhi Leonard trade, and the boys figure out the difference between Jake and Logan Paul.
